<div class = 'container'>
<h1>Delete a Donation Confirmation</h1>

<form action = '/deleteDonation' method = 'post'>
If you made a mistake in your donation form and would like to delete the confirmation form:

 <ul> <li>Enter your first name, last name, and the donation ID you received in the email sent
      after you submitted a donation form.</li>

 <li>Then press submit. </li>
</ul>
<p>A confirmation message will be emailed to you. </p>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <label for id='fname'>First name: </label><input class='form-control' text = 'text' name = 'fname' required ><br>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <label for id='lname'>Last name: </label><input class='form-control' text = 'text' name = 'lname' required ><br>
    </div>
</div>
     <label for id='donation_id' >Donation ID:  </label><input class='form-control' type='text' name = 'donation_id' required> <br>
  <input class='btn btn-outline-primary' type="submit" value = 'Submit'></input>   
    <p>     </p>
</form>
<div id = 'msg'>{{msg}}</div><br>
</div>
